reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 17, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Nice light - but clock could be better.
reviews.reviewText: Light is perfect for desk - doesn't take up alot of room and provides sufficient light for the desk. Phone charger works great and is a wonderful bonus (I have to find the sweet spot to get it to work, but that could be the phone not the Lamp - and once found its great). The only negative thing I would say is the clock is disappointing and was part of the reason for purchasing this lamp. The lamp is plugged into electricity but the clock requires a button battery for operation - meaning battery replacement will be required. Additionally there is little to no visibility to the clock. The picture above makes it appear that the clock is backlit, but when the lamp is off the clock is not visible at all. Depending on the viewing angle there is limited visibility when the lamp is on. BUT when visible you have the time, Month and Day as well as the temperature. Overall - it functions as a lamp as intended so the clock and charger are just a bonus and don't detract from it's main function.
